	<li><a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fredric_March" title="Fredric March">Fredric March</a> as Norman Maine</li>
	<li><a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adolphe_Menjou" title="Adolphe Menjou">Adolphe Menjou</a> as Oliver Niles</li>
	<li><a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/May_Robson" title="May Robson">May Robson</a> as Grandmother Lettie</li>
	<li><a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andy_Devine" title="Andy Devine">Andy Devine</a> as Daniel 'Danny' McGuire</li>
